<h1 id="toc9"><span>Hi!</span></h1>
<h2 id="toc10"><span>It's me again.</span></h2>
</div>
<h3 id="toc11"><span>Here are some facts:</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>I have a degree in Film Animation</li>
<li>I'd love to be a professional character designer but really don't have the chops for it realistically</li>
<li>my spine can bend backward at a perfect 90 degree angle</li>
<li>I'm writing an SCP podcast that updates every month</li>
<li>the first I ever heard of SCP was in 2012 when my friends and I read 087 in an abandoned paintball barricade in the woods behind my house</li>
<li>I just want everyone on this site to laugh and be happy and have a fun time</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/the-radd-zone">Check out my author page for more silly doodles!</a></p>
</div>
